{"text_id":87057,"tokens":["Long","itudinal"," studies"," often"," involve"," time","-","varying"," treatments"," and"," confound","ers",","," which"," can"," complicate"," the"," process"," of"," causal"," inference","."," This"," paper"," introduces"," history","-","restricted"," marginal"," structural"," models"," (","MS","Ms",")"," as"," a"," tool"," for"," causal"," inference"," in"," such"," studies","."," These"," models"," allow"," for"," the"," consideration"," of"," treatment"," histories"," up"," to"," a"," certain"," point"," in"," time",","," rather"," than"," the"," entire"," history","."," This"," approach"," can"," be"," particularly"," useful"," in"," situations"," where"," the"," full"," history"," is"," not"," available"," or"," is"," not"," relevant"," to"," the"," causal"," question"," at"," hand","."," We"," provide"," a"," detailed"," explanation"," of"," how"," to"," implement"," these"," models",","," as"," well"," as"," an"," examination"," of"," their"," properties","."," We"," also"," present"," a"," case"," study"," to"," illustrate"," their"," application"," in"," a"," real","-","world"," scenario","."," Our"," findings"," suggest"," that"," history","-","restricted"," MSM","s"," can"," provide"," a"," valuable"," addition"," to"," the"," toolbox"," of"," methods"," for"," causal"," inference"," in"," longitudinal"," studies","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}